Briggs & Riley

The deluxe Briggs & Riley™ brand is known for its patented Outsider® handle, a design that provides a flat packing area with more space inside the bag. Their Simple As That® guarantee provides free of charge repairs if your bag is ever broken or damaged, no proof of purchase needed, no questions asked, even if it was damaged by an airline. “Engineered for reality, guaranteed for life”.
